name: Big rainy night
description: I arrived in a country so dry, that in more than 6 years I could not be under the rain, periods of rain appear every 15 or 40 years, even one of its deserts reached 400 years without a single drop of it.  I want to be in the rain, especially when I come from a city where it rains 2 or 3 times a day.  I miss the rain and this NFT helps me remember it a bit when I used to come home on those cold and rainy nights!!
